oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry stars Roy Drusky and David Houston at the Oakland Civic Auditorium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Drusky, Roy; Houston, David, 1937-; Duke of Paducah, 1901-1986;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black on yellow) announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Roy Drusky, Duke of Paducah, David Houston, and others at the Oakland Civic Auditorium on November 23. Poster features metal photoplates of Roy Drusky, Duke of Paducah, and David Houston.
